title: Bobbysocks - Walkin' On Air (1987)
description:
Recorded in L.A. during 1987 and produced by Bill Maxwell, it was their 3rd and final album. Within four days, the album sold 50,000 copies in their native Norway (a lot for that small population country), thus it was certified Gold.

256 kbps


Bobbysocks album discography:

1984 - Bobbysocks! (re-edited in 1985 with "Let it Swing" as the opening track)
1986 - Waiting for the Morning
1987 - Walkin' on Air
2010 - The Best of Bobbysocks! (with 2 newly recorded songs)
